The City of Milan has signed the "Milan Urban Food Policy Pact" for the creation of an international network of cities in order to share a common policy on food and make its food system more equitable and sustainable.&#xd;
Here you can find the website:&#xd;
http://www.foodpolicymilano.org/urban-food-policy-pact/&#xd;
&#xd;
It is also part of the Eurocities network set up by the major European cities with the aim of sharing common challenges and opportunities at local governance level.&#xd;
Here you can find the website:&#xd;
http://www.eurocities.eu/eurocities/home
